{"lastUpdated":"2026-06-16T23:53:34.324Z","seriesId":96687,"title":"18if","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/35627795/35627795.29364597","descriptionFirst":"月城遥人は、意識と無意識の狭間―『夢世界』で目覚める。現実を拒絶し眠り続ける『眠り姫病』に陥った『電影の魔女』。彼女の欲望と希望で作り上げた夢の世界で、遥人は夢世界の研究者・神崎カツミ、謎の少女・リリィとともに魔女の本心と絶望に対面する。\n\n月城 遥人:島﨑信長／神崎 カツミ:子安武人／リリィ:名塚佳織\n\n総監修:森本晃司／シリーズ構成:冨岡淳広／キャラクターデザイン:乙幡忠志／美術設定:酒井達也／美術監督:高木佐和子／色彩設定:鈴木寿枝、佐藤祐子／デザイン監修:数井浩子／CGディレクター:長嶺明音／撮影監督:北村直樹／編集:齋藤朱里／音響監督:鶴岡陽太／音楽:阿部隆大／アニメーション制作:GONZO／原作:モブキャスト\n\n©mobcast inc./18if project\n\n次話→so35627806","tags":["GONZO","ゲーム・ソシャゲ原作","2017年夏アニメ","ホラー/サスペンス/推理"],"cours":"2017-夏","colKey":"あ","relatedSeries":[],"episodes":[{"contentId":"so35627807","episodeNo":1,"title":"18if　第1話　電影の魔女","viewCounter":1274,"commentCounter":6,"mylistCounter":31,"lengthSeconds":1419,"startTime":"2019-10-01T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/35627807/35627807.86669621"},{"contentId":"so35627806","episodeNo":2,"title":"18if　第2話　止まった時間、12才","viewCounter":312,"commentCounter":7,"mylistCounter":0,"lengthSeconds":1419,"startTime":"2019-10-01T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/35627806/35627806.59618665"},{"contentId":"so35627795","episodeNo":3,"title":"18if　第3話　初恋の魔女","viewCounter":208,"commentCounter":7,"mylistCounter":4,"lengthSeconds":1420,"startTime":"2019-10-01T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/35627795/35627795.29364597"},{"contentId":"so35627796","episodeNo":4,"title":"18if　第4話　暴食の魔女","viewCounter":159,"commentCounter":4,"mylistCounter":0,"lengthSeconds":1419,"startTime":"2019-10-01T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/35627796/35627796.95754706"},{"contentId":"so35627797","episodeNo":5,"title":"18if　第5話　凡庸の魔女","viewCounter":126,"commentCounter":6,"mylistCounter":0,"lengthSeconds":1420,"startTime":"2019-10-01T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/35627797/35627797.55878